<rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Workspaces (中文)</title><link>https://www.workspaces.xyz/</link><description>探索激发生产力的工作空间。</description><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Sat, 04 Apr 2026 15:31:09 +0000</lastBuildDate><item><title>本·弗里克</title><link>https://www.workspaces.xyz/p/131-ben-fryc</link><description>&lt;div class="_10pdwo80 dream-post-content-doc"&gt;&lt;div class="_1gqvddm0"&gt;&lt;div class="j6zgbu0"&gt;&lt;p class="dream-post-content-paragraph j6zgbu1"&gt;&lt;span class="hxnnnr0"&gt;&lt;a class="_3k8pkd0" href="https://www.benfryc.com/" rel="" target="_blank"&gt;Ben Fryc&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="hxnnnr0"&gt; 是 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="hxnnnr0"&gt;&lt;a class="_3k8pkd0" href="https://www.polywork.com/" rel="" target="_blank"&gt;Polywork&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="hxnnnr0"&gt; 的一名3D艺术家和设计师。Ben并非一直是3D艺术家，他之前是Mango Languages的产品设计师和经理。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="j6zgbu0"&gt;&lt;p class="dream-post-content-paragraph j6zgbu1"&gt;&lt;span class="hxnnnr0"&gt;在地下室工作并不意味着你不能拥有属于自己的小角落。在过去几年里，Ben布置了一个空间，在那里他为世界各地的初创公司创作风格化的艺术作品。Ben还运营着一个 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="hxnnnr0"&gt;&lt;a class="_3k8pkd0" href="https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCLmOI2PnWg8v8x4EBNgwJZA" rel="" target="_blank"&gt;小型YouTube频道&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="hxnnnr0"&gt;，致力于帮助人们学习如何使用行业标准的3D软件。你可以在 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="hxnnnr0"&gt;&lt;a class="_3k8pkd0" href="https://dribbble.com/benfryc" rel="" target="_blank"&gt;Dribbble&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="hxnnnr0"&gt;、&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="hxnnnr0"&gt;&lt;a class="_3k8pkd0" href="https://www.artstation.com/spacergifdesign" rel="" target="_blank"&gt;Artstation&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="hxnnnr0"&gt; 和 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="hxnnnr0"&gt;&lt;a class="_3k8pkd0" href="https://www.figma.com/@benfryc" rel="" target="_blank"&gt;Figma&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="hxnnnr0"&gt; 上查看他的一些作品。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="dream-post-content-imageBlock _2fealp0"&gt;&lt;div class="_2fealp1"&gt;&lt;picture&gt;&lt;source media="(max-width: 360px) and (min-resolution: 2dppx)" srcset="https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,quality=80,format=auto,width=720,onerror=redirect/uploads/asset/file/4f1bfc2e-2cba-4f4a-a9f2-865c0738571f/image.png 2x"/&gt;&lt;source media="(max-width: 360px)" srcset="https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,quality=80,format=auto,width=360,onerror=redirect/uploads/asset/file/4f1bfc2e-2cba-4f4a-a9f2-865c0738571f/image.png 1x"/&gt;&lt;source media="(max-width: 430px) and (min-resolution: 2dppx)" srcset="https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,quality=80,format=auto,width=860,onerror=redirect/uploads/asset/file/4f1bfc2e-2cba-4f4a-a9f2-865c0738571f/image.png 2x"/&gt;&lt;source media="(max-width: 430px)" srcset="https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,quality=80,format=auto,width=430,onerror=redirect/uploads/asset/file/4f1bfc2e-2cba-4f4a-a9f2-865c0738571f/image.png 1x"/&gt;&lt;img alt="" class="_2fealp2 _2fealp5" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,quality=80,format=auto,onerror=redirect/uploads/asset/file/4f1bfc2e-2cba-4f4a-a9f2-865c0738571f/image.png"/&gt;&lt;/picture&gt;&lt;div class="_1gaxnt60"&gt;&lt;small class="dream-post-content-figcaption xcryp60"&gt;&lt;/small&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class="hxnnnr0"&gt;紫色的环境光、一个辉光管时钟，以及一个漂浮在每个屏幕上的宇航员——Ben Fryc的地下工作室感觉一点也不像地下室。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="dream-post-content-imageBlock _2fealp0"&gt;&lt;div class="_2fealp1"&gt;&lt;picture&gt;&lt;source media="(max-width: 360px) and (min-resolution: 2dppx)" srcset="https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,quality=80,format=auto,width=720,onerror=redirect/uploads/asset/file/fe3ea039-c783-45a9-a59d-068e276e84f8/image.png 2x"/&gt;&lt;source media="(max-width: 360px)" srcset="https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,quality=80,format=auto,width=360,onerror=redirect/uploads/asset/file/fe3ea039-c783-45a9-a59d-068e276e84f8/image.png 1x"/&gt;&lt;source media="(max-width: 430px) and (min-resolution: 2dppx)" srcset="https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,quality=80,format=auto,width=860,onerror=redirect/uploads/asset/file/fe3ea039-c783-45a9-a59d-068e276e84f8/image.png 2x"/&gt;&lt;source media="(max-width: 430px)" srcset="https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,quality=80,format=auto,width=430,onerror=redirect/uploads/asset/file/fe3ea039-c783-45a9-a59d-068e276e84f8/image.png 1x"/&gt;&lt;img alt="" class="_2fealp2 _2fealp5" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,quality=80,format=auto,onerror=redirect/uploads/asset/file/fe3ea039-c783-45a9-a59d-068e276e84f8/image.png"/&gt;&lt;/picture&gt;&lt;div class="_1gaxnt60"&gt;&lt;small class="dream-post-content-figcaption xcryp60"&gt;&lt;/small&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class="hxnnnr0"&gt;一个经过全面处理的地下工作室——墙上有吸音板、一把Herman Miller Embody椅子，以及足够大的屏幕空间，可以同时运行Cinema4D、After Effects和Figma。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="dream-post-content-imageBlock _2fealp0"&gt;&lt;div class="_2fealp1"&gt;&lt;picture&gt;&lt;source media="(max-width: 360px) and (min-resolution: 2dppx)" srcset="https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,quality=80,format=auto,width=720,onerror=redirect/uploads/asset/file/b908579f-5121-45cd-946e-fb9444bf4931/image.png 2x"/&gt;&lt;source media="(max-width: 360px)" srcset="https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,quality=80,format=auto,width=360,onerror=redirect/uploads/asset/file/b908579f-5121-45cd-946e-fb9444bf4931/image.png 1x"/&gt;&lt;source media="(max-width: 430px) and (min-resolution: 2dppx)" srcset="https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,quality=80,format=auto,width=860,onerror=redirect/uploads/asset/file/b908579f-5121-45cd-946e-fb9444bf4931/image.png 2x"/&gt;&lt;source media="(max-width: 430px)" srcset="https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,quality=80,format=auto,width=430,onerror=redirect/uploads/asset/file/b908579f-5121-45cd-946e-fb9444bf4931/image.png 1x"/&gt;&lt;img alt="" class="_2fealp2 _2fealp5" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,quality=80,format=auto,onerror=redirect/uploads/asset/file/b908579f-5121-45cd-946e-fb9444bf4931/image.png"/&gt;&lt;/picture&gt;&lt;div class="_1gaxnt60"&gt;&lt;small class="dream-post-content-figcaption xcryp60"&gt;&lt;/small&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class="hxnnnr0"&gt;三块显示屏——两台LG 4K显示器和一块Huion Kamvas 16绘图板——中间有一系列amiibo手办守护着。3D魔法就在这里发生。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="dream-post-content-imageBlock _2fealp0"&gt;&lt;div class="_2fealp1"&gt;&lt;picture&gt;&lt;source media="(max-width: 360px) and (min-resolution: 2dppx)" srcset="https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,quality=80,format=auto,width=720,onerror=redirect/uploads/asset/file/65d0b881-5f3f-4e2f-891b-36a941220da7/image.png 2x"/&gt;&lt;source media="(max-width: 360px)" srcset="https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,quality=80,format=auto,width=360,onerror=redirect/uploads/asset/file/65d0b881-5f3f-4e2f-891b-36a941220da7/image.png 1x"/&gt;&lt;source media="(max-width: 430px) and (min-resolution: 2dppx)" srcset="https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,quality=80,format=auto,width=860,onerror=redirect/uploads/asset/file/65d0b881-5f3f-4e2f-891b-36a941220da7/image.png 2x"/&gt;&lt;source media="(max-width: 430px)" srcset="https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,quality=80,format=auto,width=430,onerror=redirect/uploads/asset/file/65d0b881-5f3f-4e2f-891b-36a941220da7/image.png 1x"/&gt;&lt;img alt="" class="_2fealp2 _2fealp5" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,quality=80,format=auto,onerror=redirect/uploads/asset/file/65d0b881-5f3f-4e2f-891b-36a941220da7/image.png"/&gt;&lt;/picture&gt;&lt;div class="_1gaxnt60"&gt;&lt;small class="dream-post-content-figcaption xcryp60"&gt;&lt;/small&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class="hxnnnr0"&gt;一个像来自另一个时代的硬件一样发光的辉光管时钟，旁边是一个说明一切的标语：&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="hxnnnr0"&gt;&lt;em&gt;Think Outside.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="hxnnnr0"&gt; Ben书桌的细节考虑得和他的3D作品一样周到。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="dream-post-content-imageBlock _2fealp0"&gt;&lt;div class="_2fealp1"&gt;&lt;picture&gt;&lt;source media="(max-width: 360px) and (min-resolution: 2dppx)" srcset="https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,quality=80,format=auto,width=720,onerror=redirect/uploads/asset/file/97dc2355-cb88-4c7c-99d8-e46036fb465e/image.png 2x"/&gt;&lt;source media="(max-width: 360px)" srcset="https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,quality=80,format=auto,width=360,onerror=redirect/uploads/asset/file/97dc2355-cb88-4c7c-99d8-e46036fb465e/image.png 1x"/&gt;&lt;source media="(max-width: 430px) and (min-resolution: 2dppx)" srcset="https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,quality=80,format=auto,width=860,onerror=redirect/uploads/asset/file/97dc2355-cb88-4c7c-99d8-e46036fb465e/image.png 2x"/&gt;&lt;source media="(max-width: 430px)" srcset="https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,quality=80,format=auto,width=430,onerror=redirect/uploads/asset/file/97dc2355-cb88-4c7c-99d8-e46036fb465e/image.png 1x"/&gt;&lt;img alt="" class="_2fealp2 _2fealp5" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,quality=80,format=auto,onerror=redirect/uploads/asset/file/97dc2355-cb88-4c7c-99d8-e46036fb465e/image.png"/&gt;&lt;/picture&gt;&lt;div class="_1gaxnt60"&gt;&lt;small class="dream-post-content-figcaption xcryp60"&gt;&lt;/small&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class="hxnnnr0"&gt;Air75键盘、罗技MX Vertical垂直鼠标，以及Ben能收集到的所有塞尔达传说amiibo——这是一个对工作和娱乐都认真对待的人的桌面。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="dream-post-content-imageBlock _2fealp0"&gt;&lt;div class="_2fealp1"&gt;&lt;picture&gt;&lt;source media="(max-width: 360px) and (min-resolution: 2dppx)" srcset="https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,quality=80,format=auto,width=720,onerror=redirect/uploads/asset/file/d676c3e3-14ea-4348-8392-dfbea5110209/image.png 2x"/&gt;&lt;source media="(max-width: 360px)" srcset="https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,quality=80,format=auto,width=360,onerror=redirect/uploads/asset/file/d676c3e3-14ea-4348-8392-dfbea5110209/image.png 1x"/&gt;&lt;source media="(max-width: 430px) and (min-resolution: 2dppx)" srcset="https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,quality=80,format=auto,width=860,onerror=redirect/uploads/asset/file/d676c3e3-14ea-4348-8392-dfbea5110209/image.png 2x"/&gt;&lt;source media="(max-width: 430px)" srcset="https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,quality=80,format=auto,width=430,onerror=redirect/uploads/asset/file/d676c3e3-14ea-4348-8392-dfbea5110209/image.png 1x"/&gt;&lt;img alt="" class="_2fealp2 _2fealp5" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,quality=80,format=auto,onerror=redirect/uploads/asset/file/d676c3e3-14ea-4348-8392-dfbea5110209/image.png"/&gt;&lt;/picture&gt;&lt;div class="_1gaxnt60"&gt;&lt;small class="dream-post-content-figcaption xcryp60"&gt;&lt;/small&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class="hxnnnr0"&gt;一个N64手柄、一台任天堂Switch、一个Polywork品牌的音箱，以及顶部的星球大战人偶——Ben书桌的右侧是一封写给那些最初让他投身创意工作的东西的情书。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p class="hynlcx0"&gt;&lt;h2 class="hynlcx1 hynlcx3" translations="[object Object]"&gt;&lt;span class="hxnnnr0"&gt;你的工作空间里有哪些物品？&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class="hynlcx0"&gt;&lt;h2 class="hynlcx1 hynlcx3" translations="[object Object]"&gt;&lt;span class="hxnnnr0"&gt;最重要的家具是什么？&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class="hynlcx0"&gt;&lt;h2 class="hynlcx1 hynlcx3" translations="[object Object]"&gt;&lt;span class="hxnnnr0"&gt;作为一名3D艺术家和设计师，你使用什么软件？&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="dream-post-content-bulletList _1ao94nj0"&gt;&lt;ul class="_1ao94nj1" translations="[object Object]"&gt;&lt;li class="_11av8sw0" translations="[object Object]"&gt;&lt;li class="_11av8sw0" translations="[object Object]"&gt;&lt;li class="_11av8sw0" translations="[object Object]"&gt;&lt;div class="j6zgbu0"&gt;&lt;p class="dream-post-content-paragraph j6zgbu1"&gt;&lt;span class="hxnnnr0"&gt;Adobe Creative Suite（主要用于After Effects）&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class="_11av8sw0" translations="[object Object]"&gt;&lt;div class="j6zgbu0"&gt;&lt;p class="dream-post-content-paragraph j6zgbu1"&gt;&lt;span class="hxnnnr0"&gt;Figma - 用于创建在Cinema4D中使用的物体形状和纹理&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class="_11av8sw0" translations="[object Object]"&gt;&lt;div class="j6zgbu0"&gt;&lt;p class="dream-post-content-paragraph j6zgbu1"&gt;&lt;span class="hxnnnr0"&gt;Greyscale Gorilla - Cinema4D的材质和插件&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p class="hynlcx0"&gt;&lt;h2 class="hynlcx1 hynlcx3" translations="[object Object]"&gt;&lt;span class="hxnnnr0"&gt;你的布置中还有哪些其他装饰？&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 20 Feb 2022 06:00:00 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>奥格·埃泽奥努</title><link>https://www.workspaces.xyz/p/128-ogeh-ezeonu</link><description>&lt;div class="_10pdwo80 dream-post-content-doc"&gt;&lt;div class="_1gqvddm0"&gt;&lt;div class="j6zgbu0"&gt;&lt;p class="dream-post-content-paragraph j6zgbu1"&gt;&lt;span class="hxnnnr0"&gt;&lt;a class="_3k8pkd0" href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/ogechukwu-ezeonu/" rel="" target="_blank"&gt;Ogeh Ezeonu&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="hxnnnr0"&gt; 是一名自由职业产品设计师，目前在 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="hxnnnr0"&gt;&lt;a class="_3k8pkd0" href="https://www.toptal.com/" rel="" target="_blank"&gt;Toptal&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="hxnnnr0"&gt; 担任高级产品设计师，负责构建和设计数字产品。她专注于为金融、娱乐、游戏和电子商务领域的产品创造以人为本的设计。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="j6zgbu0"&gt;&lt;p class="dream-post-content-paragraph j6zgbu1"&gt;&lt;span class="hxnnnr0"&gt;除了设计师的工作之外，她还喜欢听播客和有声书，创作低保真音乐，并时不时地搭建便携式相机支架。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="dream-post-content-imageBlock _2fealp0"&gt;&lt;div class="_2fealp1"&gt;&lt;picture&gt;&lt;source media="(max-width: 360px) and (min-resolution: 2dppx)" srcset="https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,quality=80,format=auto,width=720,onerror=redirect/uploads/asset/file/237ca545-74f6-4581-9cb2-1b9762f2e3fc/image.png 2x"/&gt;&lt;source media="(max-width: 360px)" srcset="https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,quality=80,format=auto,width=360,onerror=redirect/uploads/asset/file/237ca545-74f6-4581-9cb2-1b9762f2e3fc/image.png 1x"/&gt;&lt;source media="(max-width: 430px) and (min-resolution: 2dppx)" srcset="https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,quality=80,format=auto,width=860,onerror=redirect/uploads/asset/file/237ca545-74f6-4581-9cb2-1b9762f2e3fc/image.png 2x"/&gt;&lt;source media="(max-width: 430px)" srcset="https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,quality=80,format=auto,width=430,onerror=redirect/uploads/asset/file/237ca545-74f6-4581-9cb2-1b9762f2e3fc/image.png 1x"/&gt;&lt;img alt="" class="_2fealp2 _2fealp5" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,quality=80,format=auto,onerror=redirect/uploads/asset/file/237ca545-74f6-4581-9cb2-1b9762f2e3fc/image.png"/&gt;&lt;/picture&gt;&lt;div class="_1gaxnt60"&gt;&lt;small class="dream-post-content-figcaption xcryp60"&gt;&lt;/small&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class="hxnnnr0"&gt;Ogeh 的工作台布置和她设计的产品一样充满巧思：大胆的绿色墙壁、一台 LG 38 英寸超宽显示器，以及放在耳机架上的 AirPods Max。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="dream-post-content-imageBlock _2fealp0"&gt;&lt;div class="_2fealp1"&gt;&lt;picture&gt;&lt;source media="(max-width: 360px) and (min-resolution: 2dppx)" srcset="https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,quality=80,format=auto,width=720,onerror=redirect/uploads/asset/file/014b047a-89bf-4238-bbcf-53eb0ac9d0d4/image.png 2x"/&gt;&lt;source media="(max-width: 360px)" srcset="https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,quality=80,format=auto,width=360,onerror=redirect/uploads/asset/file/014b047a-89bf-4238-bbcf-53eb0ac9d0d4/image.png 1x"/&gt;&lt;source media="(max-width: 430px) and (min-resolution: 2dppx)" srcset="https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,quality=80,format=auto,width=860,onerror=redirect/uploads/asset/file/014b047a-89bf-4238-bbcf-53eb0ac9d0d4/image.png 2x"/&gt;&lt;source media="(max-width: 430px)" srcset="https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,quality=80,format=auto,width=430,onerror=redirect/uploads/asset/file/014b047a-89bf-4238-bbcf-53eb0ac9d0d4/image.png 1x"/&gt;&lt;img alt="" class="_2fealp2 _2fealp5" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,quality=80,format=auto,onerror=redirect/uploads/asset/file/014b047a-89bf-4238-bbcf-53eb0ac9d0d4/image.png"/&gt;&lt;/picture&gt;&lt;div class="_1gaxnt60"&gt;&lt;small class="dream-post-content-figcaption xcryp60"&gt;&lt;/small&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class="hxnnnr0"&gt;全貌一览——一张升降桌、一把 Haworth Fern 椅子，以及一盏专业的柔光箱灯，这意味着 Ogeh 随时都准备好上镜，无论是客户电话还是创意拍摄。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="dream-post-content-imageBlock _2fealp0"&gt;&lt;div class="_2fealp1"&gt;&lt;picture&gt;&lt;source media="(max-width: 360px) and (min-resolution: 2dppx)" srcset="https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,quality=80,format=auto,width=720,onerror=redirect/uploads/asset/file/f5d2a026-62e5-42a9-b69c-e8f64f1dffb4/image.png 2x"/&gt;&lt;source media="(max-width: 360px)" srcset="https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,quality=80,format=auto,width=360,onerror=redirect/uploads/asset/file/f5d2a026-62e5-42a9-b69c-e8f64f1dffb4/image.png 1x"/&gt;&lt;source media="(max-width: 430px) and (min-resolution: 2dppx)" srcset="https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,quality=80,format=auto,width=860,onerror=redirect/uploads/asset/file/f5d2a026-62e5-42a9-b69c-e8f64f1dffb4/image.png 2x"/&gt;&lt;source media="(max-width: 430px)" srcset="https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,quality=80,format=auto,width=430,onerror=redirect/uploads/asset/file/f5d2a026-62e5-42a9-b69c-e8f64f1dffb4/image.png 1x"/&gt;&lt;img alt="" class="_2fealp2 _2fealp5" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,quality=80,format=auto,onerror=redirect/uploads/asset/file/f5d2a026-62e5-42a9-b69c-e8f64f1dffb4/image.png"/&gt;&lt;/picture&gt;&lt;div class="_1gaxnt60"&gt;&lt;small class="dream-post-content-figcaption xcryp60"&gt;&lt;/small&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class="hxnnnr0"&gt;每个输入设备都有其专属位置——Logitech MX Keys 键盘、放在 Grovemade 胡桃木托盘上的 Apple Magic Trackpad 触控板，以及一个兼作翻页钟的 iPad。简洁、有目的性，且非常符合她的个人风格。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="dream-post-content-imageBlock _2fealp0"&gt;&lt;div class="_2fealp1"&gt;&lt;picture&gt;&lt;source media="(max-width: 360px) and (min-resolution: 2dppx)" srcset="https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,quality=80,format=auto,width=720,onerror=redirect/uploads/asset/file/49de56e0-5a79-426b-ad7c-321343effece/image.png 2x"/&gt;&lt;source media="(max-width: 360px)" srcset="https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,quality=80,format=auto,width=360,onerror=redirect/uploads/asset/file/49de56e0-5a79-426b-ad7c-321343effece/image.png 1x"/&gt;&lt;source media="(max-width: 430px) and (min-resolution: 2dppx)" srcset="https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,quality=80,format=auto,width=860,onerror=redirect/uploads/asset/file/49de56e0-5a79-426b-ad7c-321343effece/image.png 2x"/&gt;&lt;source media="(max-width: 430px)" srcset="https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,quality=80,format=auto,width=430,onerror=redirect/uploads/asset/file/49de56e0-5a79-426b-ad7c-321343effece/image.png 1x"/&gt;&lt;img alt="" class="_2fealp2 _2fealp5" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,quality=80,format=auto,onerror=redirect/uploads/asset/file/49de56e0-5a79-426b-ad7c-321343effece/image.png"/&gt;&lt;/picture&gt;&lt;div class="_1gaxnt60"&gt;&lt;small class="dream-post-content-figcaption xcryp60"&gt;&lt;/small&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class="hxnnnr0"&gt;迪特·拉姆斯紧邻漫威——Ogeh 的书架完美诠释了她的品味。严肃的设计理论与激发她创意的流行文化和谐共存。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="dream-post-content-imageBlock _2fealp0"&gt;&lt;div class="_2fealp1"&gt;&lt;picture&gt;&lt;source media="(max-width: 360px) and (min-resolution: 2dppx)" srcset="https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,quality=80,format=auto,width=720,onerror=redirect/uploads/asset/file/26df1fe0-e5c8-44f1-b9ea-6e13ea4ce780/image.png 2x"/&gt;&lt;source media="(max-width: 360px)" srcset="https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,quality=80,format=auto,width=360,onerror=redirect/uploads/asset/file/26df1fe0-e5c8-44f1-b9ea-6e13ea4ce780/image.png 1x"/&gt;&lt;source media="(max-width: 430px) and (min-resolution: 2dppx)" srcset="https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,quality=80,format=auto,width=860,onerror=redirect/uploads/asset/file/26df1fe0-e5c8-44f1-b9ea-6e13ea4ce780/image.png 2x"/&gt;&lt;source media="(max-width: 430px)" srcset="https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,quality=80,format=auto,width=430,onerror=redirect/uploads/asset/file/26df1fe0-e5c8-44f1-b9ea-6e13ea4ce780/image.png 1x"/&gt;&lt;img alt="" class="_2fealp2 _2fealp5" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,quality=80,format=auto,onerror=redirect/uploads/asset/file/26df1fe0-e5c8-44f1-b9ea-6e13ea4ce780/image.png"/&gt;&lt;/picture&gt;&lt;div class="_1gaxnt60"&gt;&lt;small class="dream-post-content-figcaption xcryp60"&gt;&lt;/small&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class="hxnnnr0"&gt;街头霸王遇见黑暗骑士——Ogeh 的书架同时也是对流行文化偶像的致敬，它们与她的设计参考书并肩而立。最好的工作空间都充满个性。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="dream-post-content-imageBlock _2fealp0"&gt;&lt;div class="_2fealp1"&gt;&lt;picture&gt;&lt;source media="(max-width: 360px) and (min-resolution: 2dppx)" srcset="https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,quality=80,format=auto,width=720,onerror=redirect/uploads/asset/file/06f59499-1c23-4e7c-a58e-6d0fa999bc06/image.png 2x"/&gt;&lt;source media="(max-width: 360px)" srcset="https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,quality=80,format=auto,width=360,onerror=redirect/uploads/asset/file/06f59499-1c23-4e7c-a58e-6d0fa999bc06/image.png 1x"/&gt;&lt;source media="(max-width: 430px) and (min-resolution: 2dppx)" srcset="https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,quality=80,format=auto,width=860,onerror=redirect/uploads/asset/file/06f59499-1c23-4e7c-a58e-6d0fa999bc06/image.png 2x"/&gt;&lt;source media="(max-width: 430px)" srcset="https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,quality=80,format=auto,width=430,onerror=redirect/uploads/asset/file/06f59499-1c23-4e7c-a58e-6d0fa999bc06/image.png 1x"/&gt;&lt;img alt="" class="_2fealp2 _2fealp5" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,quality=80,format=auto,onerror=redirect/uploads/asset/file/06f59499-1c23-4e7c-a58e-6d0fa999bc06/image.png"/&gt;&lt;/picture&gt;&lt;div class="_1gaxnt60"&gt;&lt;small class="dream-post-content-figcaption xcryp60"&gt;&lt;/small&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class="hxnnnr0"&gt;一个 Sonos Move 音箱、Vitruvi 加湿器和一幅金色边框的 ikigai（生命意义）印刷画——这是 Ogeh 工作室的一角，提醒你工作最初的意义所在。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="dream-post-content-imageBlock _2fealp0"&gt;&lt;div class="_2fealp1"&gt;&lt;picture&gt;&lt;source media="(max-width: 360px) and (min-resolution: 2dppx)" srcset="https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,quality=80,format=auto,width=720,onerror=redirect/uploads/asset/file/0fd7f9ec-4ae7-4167-87d6-87a312a229ba/image.png 2x"/&gt;&lt;source media="(max-width: 360px)" srcset="https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,quality=80,format=auto,width=360,onerror=redirect/uploads/asset/file/0fd7f9ec-4ae7-4167-87d6-87a312a229ba/image.png 1x"/&gt;&lt;source media="(max-width: 430px) and (min-resolution: 2dppx)" srcset="https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,quality=80,format=auto,width=860,onerror=redirect/uploads/asset/file/0fd7f9ec-4ae7-4167-87d6-87a312a229ba/image.png 2x"/&gt;&lt;source media="(max-width: 430px)" srcset="https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,quality=80,format=auto,width=430,onerror=redirect/uploads/asset/file/0fd7f9ec-4ae7-4167-87d6-87a312a229ba/image.png 1x"/&gt;&lt;img alt="" class="_2fealp2 _2fealp5" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,quality=80,format=auto,onerror=redirect/uploads/asset/file/0fd7f9ec-4ae7-4167-87d6-87a312a229ba/image.png"/&gt;&lt;/picture&gt;&lt;div class="_1gaxnt60"&gt;&lt;small class="dream-post-content-figcaption xcryp60"&gt;&lt;/small&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class="hxnnnr0"&gt;当设计工作完成后，这个角落就派上用场了——摄影器材、一把原声吉他、一张奶油色扶手椅，以及每面墙上的艺术品。Ogeh 的工作室是为完整的创意生活而打造的。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p class="hynlcx0"&gt;&lt;h2 class="hynlcx1 hynlcx3" translations="[object Object]"&gt;&lt;span class="hxnnnr0"&gt;你的工作空间里有哪些物品？&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class="hynlcx0"&gt;&lt;h2 class="hynlcx1 hynlcx3" translations="[object Object]"&gt;&lt;span class="hxnnnr0"&gt;作为产品设计师，你使用哪些软件？&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 12 Feb 2022 06:00:00 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>维克托·弗拉赫克（Ekaeoq）</title><link>https://www.workspaces.xyz/p/526-viktor-vlahek-ekaeoq</link><description>&lt;div class="dream-post-content-quote _1xtprv90" translations="[object Object]"&gt;&lt;p class="_1xtprv91"&gt;❝&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="j6zgbu0"&gt;&lt;p class="dream-post-content-paragraph j6zgbu1"&gt;&lt;span class="hxnnnr0"&gt;我并不真的认为你能“激发”创造力。我认为创造力是随着时间积累起来的，是通过多年观察事物、吸收激励你的东西，并慢慢发展出你自己的品味和思维方式而形成的。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="j6zgbu0"&gt;&lt;p class="dream-post-content-paragraph j6zgbu1"&gt;&lt;span class="hxnnnr0"&gt;但最重要的是，我认为它来自于工作，来自于开始、尝试、失败、调整和再次尝试。我能想起很多次，我在过度思考某件事上浪费了太多时间，而真正的解决方案其实只是开始，测试什么有效，看看什么无效。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="j6zgbu0"&gt;&lt;p class="dream-post-content-paragraph j6zgbu1"&gt;&lt;span class="hxnnnr0"&gt;所以对我来说，“激发”创造力的唯一真正方法是行动起来，开始工作，并不断迭代，直到你对自己创造的东西感到满意。这几乎适用于生活的方方面面。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 04 Apr 2026 15:31:09 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>布雷特·杰克逊</title><link>https://www.workspaces.xyz/p/525-brett-jackson</link><description>&lt;div class="dream-post-content-quote _1xtprv90" translations="[object Object]"&gt;&lt;p class="_1xtprv91"&gt;❝&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="j6zgbu0"&gt;&lt;p class="dream-post-content-paragraph j6zgbu1"&gt;&lt;span class="hxnnnr0"&gt;我喜欢从容地度过早晨，我会煮点咖啡，在书桌前坐下，规划好一天的事务，并在开始工作前画些草图。我的日常习惯相当固定，所以悠闲的早晨是让我一天顺利开始的必要条件。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 28 Mar 2026 14:20:27 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>帕特里克·摩根</title><link>https://www.workspaces.xyz/p/219-patrick-morgan</link><description>&lt;div class="dream-post-content-quote _1xtprv90" translations="[object Object]"&gt;&lt;p class="_1xtprv91"&gt;❝&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="j6zgbu0"&gt;&lt;p class="dream-post-content-paragraph j6zgbu1"&gt;&lt;span class="hxnnnr0"&gt;我个人发现，从那些与我的工作有间接关联的事物中，我能获得更多的能量和灵感，所以我总是从其他领域汲取养分：行为经济学、哲学、城市规划、耐力运动、音乐制作，这个列表可以一直列下去……所以，我可能只需要稍微转换一下话题，就能解锁一个新的想法。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span class="hxnnnr0"&gt;或者，我使用的另一个策略是，设定一个完全任意的限制来强迫自己行动。就像我曾经做过一个练习，决定在我25岁生日之前，在25周内创作并录制25首歌。这听起来可能有点傻，但我已经明白，只要我能让自己开始并积累一些动力，迟早会有好事发生。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 20 Nov 2022 06:00:00 +0000</pubDate></item></channel></rss>